Package: checkmk-downtime-service
Version: 1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: systemd, curl
Maintainer: Marc Risse <risse@risse-it.de>
Description: CheckMK downtime service for automatic maintenance windows
 Automatically sets CheckMK downtimes during system shutdown/reboot
 to prevent false alerts during planned maintenance.
 .
 This package includes systemd integration for reliable operation
 and secure configuration management.
